FORMAT: 1A
HOST: http://localhost:3456

# Sava.io API
Dokumentasi API untuk sistem perbankan premium Sava.io. 
Semua request manipulasi data menggunakan metode POST untuk keamanan tambahan.

## Authentication [/api/auth]

### Login [POST /api/auth/login]
Masuk ke sistem untuk mendapatkan access token.

+ Request (application/json)

            {
                "username": "admin",
                "password": "password"
            }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

            {
                "access_token": "YWRtaW46YWNjZXNz...",
                "user": {
                    "username": "admin",
                    "role": "admin"
                }
            }

## Nasabah [/api/customers]

### List Nasabah [POST /api/customers/list]
Mengambil semua daftar nasabah.

+ Request (application/json)

            {}

+ Response 200 (application/json)

            {
                "data": [
                    { "id": 1, "name": "Budi Santoso" },
                    { "id": 2, "name": "Siti Aminah" }
                ],
                "total": 2
            }

### Tambah Nasabah [POST /api/customers/create]
Menambah nasabah baru ke sistem.

+ Request (application/json)

            {
                "name": "Jane Doe"
            }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

            { "id": 3, "name": "Jane Doe" }

## Rekening [/api/accounts]

### List Rekening [POST /api/accounts/list]
Daftar semua rekening aktif.

+ Request (application/json)

            {}

+ Response 200 (application/json)

            {
                "data": [
                    { 
                        "id": 1, 
                        "account_id": "ACC-001", 
                        "customer_id": 1, 
                        "balance": 5000000 
                    }
                ]
            }

## Transaksi [/api/transactions]

### Buat Transaksi [POST /api/transactions/create]
Melakukan setoran (DEPOSIT) atau penarikan (WITHDRAW).

+ Request (application/json)

            {
                "account_id": 1,
                "transaction_type": "DEPOSIT",
                "amount": 1000000,
                "transaction_date": "2024-05-01"
            }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

            {
                "id": 101,
                "status": "success",
                "amount": 1000000,
                "ending_balance": 6000000
            }